Transmutation
Levels: Paladin 1, Ranger 1
Components: V, S
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Instant

You make a single attack that deals double damage to your foe. You also take a -2 penalty to your AC for 6 seconds.

A paladin uses their smite evil ability with this attack if they have at least one use remaining and the target is evil.

<i>A violent fury consumes you. You seek nothing more than to charge at your enemies and bash in their heads.</i>